Package managers

Class ManagerFactory

java.lang.Object
managers.ManagerFactory
public class ManagerFactory
extends java.lang.Object
Wrapper class for managers. Managers aren't created one by one separately, All existing managers all this class' fields. they are created together.

22.06.2020.
